Tributes continue to pour in for Vukani 'Chilli M' Masinga. Former colleague, DJ Sbu speaks about the life of the veteran DJ. #Rundown Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Tributes continue to pour in for Vukani 'Chilli M' Masinga. Musician and producer Sbusiso Leope (also known as DJ Sbu) says Masinga is his number one radio personality.
"To start the year like this, losing a friend, colleague, brother and somebody I started radio with is quite sad and more so for his family and children." The veteran radio jock died at a Johannesburg hospital on Thursday. Masinga was rushed to the hospital for an undisclosed illness. Watch the full interview with DJ Sbu in the video above.